                    </p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-default btn-lg" href="~/Home/About">About Us &raquo;</a></p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <img src="~/Content/Images/ideaImage.jpg" style=" width:95%;height:115%" />
                    <h2>Careers</h2>
                    <p>We are constantly looking for new talent and hope you'll join us in making top notch products to meet our clients' needs.</p>
